PSCT.Base: If a "Sky Striker Ace" monster(s) is Normal or Special Summoned, except "Sky Striker Ace - Roze" (except during the Damage Step): You can Special Summon this card from your hand. You can only use each effect of "Sky Striker Ace - Roze" once per turn.
